text: Great Canfield is a village and civil parish in Uttlesford, Essex, England. In 2001 there were 364 people living in Great Canfield. It has a church called St Mary. It includes the hamlets of Hope End Green, Canfield Hart, Bacon End and Green Street.http://www.recordinguttlesfordhistory.org.uk/great%20canfield/great%20canfield.html == References == Category:Uttlesford Category:Villages in Essex Category:Civil parishes in Essex
